===Noun===
'''[[royal]] [[jelly]]'''

#A substance [[secrete]]d by [[bee]]s to aid in the development of [[immature]] or [[young]] bees, called royal jelly because it is supplied in extra measure to those young that will become [[queen bee]]s.

